<Window x:Class="KingdomHeartsMusicPatcher.CreditsWindow"
        xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml/presentation"
        xmlns:x="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml"
        Title="Credits" Height="480" Width="820"
        WindowStartupLocation="CenterOwner"
        ResizeMode="CanResize"
        Background="#FF252526" Foreground="White"
        FontFamily="Segoe UI">
  <FlowDocumentScrollViewer VerticalScrollBarVisibility="Auto" Padding="20" IsToolBarVisible="False" IsSelectionEnabled="True" FontFamily="Segoe UI">
    <FlowDocument Background="Transparent" Foreground="White" FontFamily="Segoe UI" FontSize="13">
      <Paragraph FontSize="22" FontWeight="Bold" Foreground="#FF007ACC">Credits &amp; Thanks</Paragraph>

      <Paragraph FontSize="13">
        Kingdom Hearts Music Patcher (KHMP) exists thanks to these tools and the people who developed them:
      </Paragraph>

      <Paragraph FontSize="13">
        <Run Text="- KHPCSoundTools "/>
        <Run Text="("/>
        <Hyperlink NavigateUri="https://github.com/Leinxad/KHPCSoundTools" RequestNavigate="Hyperlink_RequestNavigate">https://github.com/Leinxad/KHPCSoundTools</Hyperlink>
        <Run Text=")"/>
      </Paragraph>

      <List MarkerStyle="Disc">
        <ListItem>
          <Paragraph FontSize="13">
            <Hyperlink NavigateUri="https://github.com/AntonioDePau" RequestNavigate="Hyperlink_RequestNavigate">AntonioDePau</Hyperlink>
          </Paragraph>
        </ListItem>
        <ListItem>
          <Paragraph FontSize="13">
            <Hyperlink NavigateUri="https://github.com/danvelezsan" RequestNavigate="Hyperlink_RequestNavigate">danvelezsan</Hyperlink>
          </Paragraph>
        </ListItem>
        <ListItem>
          <Paragraph FontSize="13">
            <Hyperlink NavigateUri="https://github.com/o0DemonBoy0o" RequestNavigate="Hyperlink_RequestNavigate">DemonBoy</Hyperlink>
          </Paragraph>
        </ListItem>
        <ListItem>
          <Paragraph FontSize="13">
            <Hyperlink NavigateUri="https://github.com/Leinxad" RequestNavigate="Hyperlink_RequestNavigate">Leinxad</Hyperlink>
          </Paragraph>
        </ListItem>
      </List>

      <Paragraph FontSize="13" Margin ="30 0 0 0">
        KHMP emulates the SingleEncoder implementation available at
        <Hyperlink NavigateUri="https://github.com/Leinxad/KHPCSoundTools/tree/main/SingleEncoder" RequestNavigate="Hyperlink_RequestNavigate">
          https://github.com/Leinxad/KHPCSoundTools/tree/main/SingleEncoder
        </Hyperlink>.
        Thanks to KHPCSoundTools' documentation, track lists and the exact paths where each specific track must be placed when generating patches were obtained.
        The KH1, KH2, KH:BBS, KH:ReCOM and KH:DDD lists can be found here:
        <Hyperlink NavigateUri="https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1JMAhUSeEf3r-njF2-8EBX8mUDVa0xaLs/edit?gid=1851343023#gid=1851343023" RequestNavigate="Hyperlink_RequestNavigate">
          Google Sheets (track lists)
        </Hyperlink>.
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph FontSize="13" Margin ="30 10 0 0">
        The “chronological order” referred to in the default option configured in the track ordering combo corresponds to the order in which the songs are listed in these official YouTube playlists (for example,
        <Hyperlink NavigateUri="https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=OLAK5uy_n_kAUk8IBMPh3lx0w9VsWptrA2vK-9WME" RequestNavigate="Hyperlink_RequestNavigate">
          this one for KH1
        </Hyperlink>).
        This order matches the order in which the songs are first heard while progressing through the game’s story.
        If you notice that a song is out of place, it is possible, as this order has not been thoroughly reviewed.
      </Paragraph>

      <Paragraph FontSize="13">
        <Run Text="- KHPCPatchManager "/>
        <Run Text="("/>
        <Hyperlink NavigateUri="https://github.com/AntonioDePau/KHPCPatchManager" RequestNavigate="Hyperlink_RequestNavigate">https://github.com/AntonioDePau/KHPCPatchManager</Hyperlink>
        <Run Text=")"/>
      </Paragraph>

      <List MarkerStyle="Disc">
        <ListItem>
          <Paragraph FontSize="13">
            <Hyperlink NavigateUri="https://github.com/AntonioDePau" RequestNavigate="Hyperlink_RequestNavigate">AntonioDePau</Hyperlink>
          </Paragraph>
        </ListItem>
      </List>

      <Paragraph FontSize="13" Margin ="30 0 0 0">
        KHPCPatchManager is essential because it performs the actual application of generated patches and enables modifying the game's installed files. KHPCPatchManager is embedded within KHMP.
      </Paragraph>

      <Paragraph FontSize="13">
        <Run Text="- Sonic Music Mods, by "/>
        <Hyperlink NavigateUri="https://next.nexusmods.com/profile/SpaceBoiStreams/mods" RequestNavigate="Hyperlink_RequestNavigate">SpaceBoiStreams</Hyperlink>
        <Run Text=". These mods have served as guidance to be able to evaluate the patches created by KHMP and to check whether paths, packaging, and file names were correct."/>
      </Paragraph>

      <Paragraph FontSize="13">
        <Run Text="- KingdomSaveEditor"/>
        <Run Text="("/>
        <Hyperlink NavigateUri="https://github.com/Xeeynamo/KingdomSaveEditor" RequestNavigate="Hyperlink_RequestNavigate">https://github.com/Xeeynamo/KingdomSaveEditor</Hyperlink>
        <Run Text="), used for testing all games."/>
      </Paragraph>

      <List MarkerStyle="Disc">
        <ListItem>
          <Paragraph FontSize="13">
            <Hyperlink NavigateUri="https://github.com/Xeeynamo/KingdomSaveEditor/graphs/contributors" RequestNavigate="Hyperlink_RequestNavigate">Xeeynamo and other contributors</Hyperlink>
          </Paragraph>
        </ListItem>
      </List>

      <Paragraph FontSize="13">
        <Run Text="- 100% Save Files, by Matthew_Niverse"/>
        <Run Text="("/>
        <Hyperlink NavigateUri="https://www.reddit.com/r/KingdomHearts/comments/qewjfe/100_save_files_for_kingdom_hearts_1_recom_2_bbs/" RequestNavigate="Hyperlink_RequestNavigate">Reddit post</Hyperlink>
        <Run Text=")"/>
      </Paragraph>

      <Paragraph FontSize="13">
        <Run Text="- Kingdom Hearts Music Patcher ("/>
        <Hyperlink NavigateUri="https://github.com/jmtdev0/KingdomHeartsCustomMusic" RequestNavigate="Hyperlink_RequestNavigate">https://github.com/jmtdev0/KingdomHeartsCustomMusic</Hyperlink>
        <Run Text=") was developed by "/>
        <Hyperlink NavigateUri="https://github.com/jmtdev0" RequestNavigate="Hyperlink_RequestNavigate">jmtdev0</Hyperlink>
        <Run Text=" with the goal of making it really easy for the Kingdom Hearts community to replace original soundtrack tracks and have a fun time unleashing their creativity. Naturally, anyone is welcome to use this application, share it, create content with it, or even develop new versions from it."/>
      </Paragraph>

      <Paragraph FontSize="13" Margin ="30 0 0 0">
        <Run Text="A perhaps ambitious idea for the future of this project could be integrating it with every game listed in this document "/>
        <Hyperlink NavigateUri="https://www.twitch.tv/sonicshadowsilver2" RequestNavigate="Hyperlink_RequestNavigate">Sonicshadowsilver2</Hyperlink>
        <Run Text="elaborated: "/>
        <Hyperlink NavigateUri="https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1-NfkF8It6kt6P2ZIppO1FLzLqZye3RMaOJU79_BbAuo/edit?gid=1689200989#gid=1689200989" RequestNavigate="Hyperlink_RequestNavigate">
          KH2FM PC Music Rando - Custom Song Packs
        </Hyperlink>
      </Paragraph>

      <Paragraph FontSize="12" Foreground="#FFAAAAAA">
        This tool is not affiliated with Square Enix or Disney. For recreational and modding purposes only.
      </Paragraph>
    </FlowDocument>
  </FlowDocumentScrollViewer>
</Window>